OL,5, Ovo Energy customers have been hit with
OL,6, bills of up to #116,000 for a month's  
OL,7, energy, the BBC has found.             
OL,9,FCustomers have claimed their energy    
OL,10,Fusage has been miscalculated after     
OL,11,Ftransferring over to the energy giant  
OL,12,For having a smart meter installed.     
OL,14,FSome of their complaints have been     
OL,15,Fupheld by the energy ombudsman yet they
OL,16,Fare still waiting for their account    
OL,17,Fdebt to be recalculated.               
OL,19,F"We are very sorry for shortfalls in   
OL,20,Fservice," said an Ovo spokesperson.    
